<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />

  <title>회원가입 - SchoolHub</title>

  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/common.css" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/post-new.css" />
</head>
<body>
  <%- include("../partials/header", { school: null }) %>

  <main class="container">
    <a href="/" class="back-link">← 메인으로 돌아가기</a>

    <h1>회원가입</h1>
    <p>SchoolHub 계정을 만들면 로그인 상태에서 본인 닉네임으로 글과 댓글을 작성할 수 있습니다.</p>

    <% if (error) { %>
      <div class="error-box"><%= error %></div>
    <% } %>

    <form action="/register" method="POST" class="post-form">
      <label>
        닉네임
        <input
          type="text"
          name="nickname"
          autocomplete="nickname"
          value="<%= form.nickname %>"
          placeholder="예: 동윤"
          maxlength="20"
          required
        />
      </label>

      <label>
        이메일
        <input
          type="email"
          name="email"
          autocomplete="email"
          value="<%= form.email %>"
          placeholder="example@email.com"
          required
        />
      </label>

      <label>
        비밀번호
        <input
          type="password"
          name="password"
          autocomplete="new-password"
          placeholder="6자 이상"
          required
        />
      </label>

      <label>
        비밀번호 확인
        <input
          type="password"
          name="passwordConfirm"
          autocomplete="new-password"
          placeholder="비밀번호를 한 번 더 입력"
          required
        />
      </label>

      <button type="submit">회원가입</button>
    </form>
  </main>

  <%- include("../partials/footer") %>
</body>
</html>